tonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 18, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bhc1665702625956.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bhc1665702625956.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bhc1665702625956.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bhc1665702625956\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n /iap\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"bhc1665702625956___iap_485819\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Compile all the specified development objects, regardless of their purpose (Normal, Palettes, and Templates).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__topic_d107727e1_d107728e1_d107729e1_d107730e1_d107731e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d894393e49\">\n                  \n Used With\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__d6347e22\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yqf1665702625882.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yqf1665702625882.html\" title=\"Compile application shells.\">/aps or /app</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__d6347e27\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sww1665702625667.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sww1665702625667.html\" title=\"Compile all types of compilable main development objects, including components, modeled entities, and global objects.\">/all</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__d6347e32\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifp1665702626096.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifp1665702626096.html\" title=\"Compile all components, including server pages, HTML forms, forms, reports, services, entity services, and session services.\">/cpt</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__d6347e37\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ars1665702626915.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ars1665702626915.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface entity service components.\">/esv</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__d6347e42\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rtz1665702626248.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtz1665702626248.html\" title=\"Compile dynamic server pages.\">/dsp</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__d6347e48\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fvm1665702627074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fvm1665702627074.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface form components.\">/frm</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__d6347e53\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ixo1665702655853.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ixo1665702655853.html\" title=\"Compile global ProcScript and variables in a library.\">/lib</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__d6347e58\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxo1665702656136.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxo1665702656136.html\" title=\"Compile menu bars, menus, and menu items.\">/men</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__d6347e63\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kjb1665702652886.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kjb1665702652886.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface report components.\">/rpt</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__d6347e68\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"umc1665702653094.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/umc1665702653094.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface session service components.\">/ssv</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__d6347e73\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gku1665702653234.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gku1665702653234.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface service components.\">/svc</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__d6347e79\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"prm1665702626469.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/prm1665702626469.html\" title=\"Compile static server pages.\">/usp</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__topic_d107732e1_d107733e1_d107734e1_d107735e1_d107736e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d894393e180\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__p_d149582e1_d149583e1_d149584e1\">By default, when compiling main development objects using command line switches (such as <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/all</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/cpt</span>, and so on), only objects that have the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Purpose</span> property set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">N (Normal)</code> are compiled.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bhc1665702625956__p_d149585e1_d149586e1_d149587e1\">Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/iap</span> (include all purposes) sub-switch when you want to compile templates and palettes as well as normal development objects.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xfc1665702625593.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Compiling from the IDE Command Line</a><p>The IDE command line can be used to compile multiple objects without opening the IDE. It is especially useful for automating compilation by means of batch scripts.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526048\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526048\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/iap Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 18, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /iap Compile all the specified development objects, regardless of their purpose (Normal, Palettes, and Templates). Used With /aps or /app /all /cpt /esv /dsp /frm /lib /men /rpt /ssv /svc /usp Description By default, when compiling main development objects using command line switches (such as /all , /cpt , and so on), only objects that have the Purpose property set to N (Normal) are compiled. Use the /iap (include all purposes) sub-switch when you want to compile templates and palettes as well as normal development objects. Related Links Compiling from the IDE Command Line The IDE command line can be used to compile multiple objects without opening the IDE. It is especially useful for automating compilation by means of batch scripts. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}